OL,4,CMan bullied by youths jailed for
OL,5,Cthrowing bleach
OL,6, A man who was being bullied by a group
OL,7, of teenagers has been jailed for
OL,8, throwing a bottle of bleach at them.
OL,10,FDaniel Henderson, 28, was homeless and
OL,11,Fliving in a tent when the incident
OL,12,Fhappened in Plymouth city centre on 31
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,FHe admitted having the bleach bottle as
OL,16,Fan offensive weapon and was jailed for
OL,17,F144 days at Plymouth Crown Court.
OL,19,FJudge Robert Linford said Henderson was
OL,20,Fbeing "treated outrageously" but
OL,21,F"reacted stupidly and dangerously".
